Import Data

library(readr)

## Parsed with column specification:

nifty50
# data <- nifty50[sample(nrow(nifty50), 3000),]
data <- nifty50[1:1000,]

Initialize plot

plot1 <- ggplot(data = data,
          mapping = aes(x = date, y = close))
plot1

Plot points

plot11 <- plot1 +
          geom_point()
plot11
